com.ninja_squad.dbsetup.generator

Class DateSequenceValueGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ninja_squad.dbsetup.generator.DateSequenceValueGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ValueGenerator<java.time.ZonedDateTime>

    public final class DateSequenceValueGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
implements ValueGenerator<java.time.ZonedDateTime>
    A ValueGenerator that returns a sequence of dates, starting at a given zoned date time and incremented by a given time, specified as an increment and a temporal unit.
